QuestData.Title: Awakening the Archdruid
QuestData.Description: Now, we must focus our efforts on waking Archdruid Steelclaw.$B$BShe and our druid brethren slumber in the barrow dens to the south.$B$BWith the furbolgs quelled, we can pass safely to the entrance.$B$BGo and awaken the Archdruid. I pray to Elune that we are not too late.
QuestData.LogDescription: Awaken the Archdruid of the Claw.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Speak to Archdruid Koda Steelclaw in the Sleeper's Barrow.
QuestData.RewardText: <The Archdruid's deep, shallow breaths rumble across the chamber.>
